items.subject: Sv: Stacky's funding round <> EasyVC

body.text:
Hi Daniel,

I hope all is well.

I can see the benefit of using AI to dig into investor lists etc.

We're currently preparing a round for Q2 and are working with a Swedish corp there, but would be intresting to know how your model works.

I guess the info you have found about us is quite old so needs to be updated in order to produce any useful results.

Brgds



________________________________
Från: Daniel Olmedo <daniel@easyvcai.site>
Skickat: den 9 december 2025 09:24
Till: Stefan Olsson, stefan@stackys.com <stefan@stackys.com>
Ämne: Stacky's funding round <> EasyVC

CAUTION: This email originated from outside of JDI.

Hey Stefan,

Saw that you guys raised more than a year ago, usually a sign that you’re in (or about to be in) fundraising mode for Stacky's again.

EasyVC uses AI to help you:
- Identify the right investors across +50,000 VCs & angels
- Rank them by thesis, stage, geography, and portfolio fit
- Automate outreach to portfolio founders for warm intros
- Create momentum and FOMO in the round

We have founders that raised their last funding round in less than 3 months using our tool.

Can I send you a sample of the type of investor data that our AI can generate for Stacky's?

Best,

Daniel Olmedo
Co-Founder of EasyVC ai
